main event: Four objects were observed in the sky over Fort Meyers, Florida on September 4, 1957.
interesting points: The objects were seen in different directions: two in the south, one in the east, and one in the north., The objects were stationary on and off for over an hour., The duration of the observation was over one hour., There is no official report in file regarding this sighting., There are photos associated with this sighting.
